Imagery Description: Draped woman leaning forward, resting right arm on tambourine, to nude longNon Sepcifiedhaired youth seated to right, with head turned back towards her, resting right hand on tambourine. Branch between them (cf. nos. 14 and 50). Cf. with lebes gamikos 4831 (no. 20, from Gaudo T. 3); found with five other vases attributed to this painter.
